In [11]:
edges$Family <- gsub('-.*','',edges$TE)

abundance_in_our_genomes <- as.data.frame(table(edges$TE))
abundance_in_our_genomes$Part <- abundance_in_our_genomes$Freq/143*100
options(repr.plot.width = 5, repr.plot.height = 5)
tesubfamily_freq_by_genome <- ggplot(abundance_in_our_genomes,aes(Part))+
    geom_histogram(position='identity',fill="#d95f02",alpha=0.5,binwidth=5)+
    theme_minimal(base_size=20)+
    labs(x="Occurence in Genomes [%]",y="Frequency")+
    theme(text=element_text(size=15,family="Times New Roman"))+
    geom_vline(xintercept = 100, linetype="dashed", 
                color = "darkgrey",size=0.5)+
    annotate("text",x=100,y=53,label="Gypsy",family="Times New Roman")

nodes_freq<-as.data.frame(table(nodes$Family))
head(nodes_freq[order(nodes_freq$Freq,decreasing=T),],5)


options(scipen=10000)
options(repr.plot.width = 5, repr.plot.height = 5)
node_number_by_te_family <-  ggplot(nodes_freq,aes(Freq))+
    geom_histogram(position='identity',fill="#d95f02",alpha=0.5,binwidth=500)+theme_grey(base_size=20)+
    labs(x="Number of Nodes",y="Frequency")+
    theme_minimal(base_size=20)+
    theme(text=element_text(size=15,family="Times New Roman"))+
    geom_vline(xintercept = nodes_freq[nodes_freq$Var1=='Gypsy',]$Freq, linetype="dashed", 
                color = "darkgrey",size=0.5)+
    annotate("text",x=10020,y=5,label="Gypsy",family="Times New Roman")

Figure EV8c¶

In [5]:
edges_summary <- edges %>% 
                group_by(Family) %>% 
                        summarise(mean_count=mean(Weight_count),
                                  mean_length=mean(Weight_length),
                                  median_count=median(Weight_count),
                                  median_length=median(Weight_length))


temedianlength_by_tesubfamily <-ggplot(edges_summary,aes(median_length))+
    geom_histogram(position='identity',fill="#d95f02",alpha=0.5,binwidth=10000)+theme_minimal(base_size=20)+
    labs(x="Median Coverage per Genome [bp]",y="Frequency")+
    theme(text=element_text(size=15,family="Times New Roman"))+
    geom_vline(xintercept = edges_summary[edges_summary$Family=='Gypsy',]$median_length, linetype="dashed", 
                color = "darkgrey",size=0.5)+
    annotate("text",x=836000,y=2,label="Copia",family="Times New Roman")+
    annotate("text",x=758000,y=2,label="Gypsy",family="Times New Roman")


temedianlength_by_tesubfamily

degree_z<- ggplot(gypsy_jk,aes(x=reorder(ID,Degree_z),y=Degree_z))+
    geom_bar(stat='identity',aes(fill=Color))+theme_minimal(base_size=10)+
    labs(y='Degree Z-scores',x='TE Family',fill='')+theme(legend.position='bottom')+
    theme(text=element_text(size=15,family="Times New Roman"),
           axis.text.y = element_text(size = 10,family="Times New Roman"),
            legend.text=element_text(size=15,family="Times New Roman"))+
     coord_flip()+
     scale_fill_jco()
